blishment of long-term, potentially personalised, relations between individuals belonging to different species?\nDomestication has given rise to new interspecific forms of communication, cooperation and social cognition (unlike chimpanzees, dogs, goats, horses are receptive to intentional communication): what are the common grounds and the codes on which communication between codomestic species are established? How do animals cooperate in riding, working, milking and what is the role of those cooperations in the domestication process?[:]\n\n</div>\n\n\n\n";s:20:"text_selected_editor";s:4:"html";s:5:"autop";b:1;s:12:"_sow_form_id";s:13:"56d5ba2ac014d";s:11:"panels_info";a:6:{s:5:"class";s:31:"SiteOrigin_Widget_Editor_Widget";s:3:"raw";b:0;s:4:"grid";i:3;s:4:"cell";i:1;s:2:"id";i:7;s:5:"style";a:1:{s:18:"background_display";s:4:"tile";}}}}s:5:"grids";a:4:{i:0;a:2:{s:5:"cells";i:1;s:5:"style";a:4:{s:5:"align";b:1;s:11:"row_stretch";s:4:"full";s:5:"class";s:13:"classaccroche";s:14:"column_padding";s:0:"";}}i:1;a:2:{s:5:"cells";i:2;s:5:"style";a:2:{s:5:"align";b:1;s:14:"column_padding";s:0:"";}}i:2;a:2:{s:5:"cells";i:1;s:5:"style";a:0:{}}i:3;a:2:{s:5:"cells";i:2;s:5:"style";a:6:{s:7:"padding";s:4:"15px";s:5:"align";s:0:"";s:10:"background";s:7:"#368c05";s:11:"row_stretch";s:4:"full";s:5:"class";s:17:"classrowtextelong";s:14:"column_padding";b:1;}}}s:10:"grid_cells";a:6:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:"grid";i:0;s:6:"weight";i:1;}i:1;a:2:{s:4:"grid";i:1;s:6:"weight";d:0.40016638935108001;}i:2;a:2:{s:4:"grid";i:1;s:6:"weight";d:0.59983361064892005;}i:3;a:2:{s:4:"grid";i:2;s:6:"weight";i:1;}i:4;a:2:{s:4:"grid";i:3;s:6:"weight";d:0.5;}i:5;a:2:{s:4:"grid";i:3;s:6:"weight";d:0.5;}}}'),
